                <mxCell id="15" value="" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-120" y="80" width="360" height="280" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="16" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(246, 246, 246)); font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;Summary&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Mona Sans VF&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;You are a blob of nanobots of a tiny size (between microscopic and golf ball) The goal is to escape the lab by going through walls and other stuff (hence borders) losing mass in the progress. You will need to conserve mass to stay alive and other things that reduce mass include heat spots, electricity, and other nano bot blobs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-100" y="100" width="320" height="240" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="20" style="edgeStyle=none;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="17" target="18">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="17" value="Research new techs like splitting and merging" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="810" y="160" width="140" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="21" style="edgeStyle=none;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="18" target="11">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="18" value="Upgrade your max mass, speed, concentration, etc." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="970" y="160" width="140" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="22" value="" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-120" y="400" width="360" height="280" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="24" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;Technical Details&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;- Top Down View&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; - Should have option for keyboard only&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; - Speed depends on mass&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; - Squeezing doesn&#39;t reduce mass&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-100" y="420" width="320" height="240" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="25" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Controls&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(240, 246, 252); transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;Move:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;W, A, S, D&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; transition: none !important; margin-top: 0.25em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;Aim:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Mouse Cursor&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; transition: none !important; margin-top: 0.25em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;Phase:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Hold Left-Click&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; transition: none !important; margin-top: 0.25em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;Dash / Squeeze:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Spacebar&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; transition: none !important; margin-top: 0.25em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;Split:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Z Key&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; transition: none !important; margin-top: 0.25em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;Shoot:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Left-Click&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="300" y="340" width="240" height="320" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="26" value="" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-120" y="720" width="1000" height="690" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="28" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 102));&quot;&gt;Levels&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;The levels are somewhat close to how portal works, in whcih for the first few levels you are in a lab with relatively random objects that you have to navigate through, while the remaining ones are inside lab equipment and the like. Each level is very small, requiring only 1-2 min of playtime, and the initial levels should be straightforward&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 1 - 2 tutorial levels, introducing basic controls like Move and Aim&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 3 core idea, phase is unlocked, introducing mass&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 4 play around with phase&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 5 first glimpse at traps, introduce hot spot, also introding the relation between size and mass&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 6 core idea, dash/squeeze, introducing phase consumption metrics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 7 play around with current ideas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 8 introduce button, enabling certain actions to happen such as opening gateways&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 9 introduce electric net, traps nanobots instead of killing them freeing them would require disabling the grid&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 10 introduce neutral blobs, allowing you to increase your mass using them&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 11 introduce the weighted button, requiring a specific amount of weight to work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 12 play around with current ideas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 13 introduce watcher and enemy nanobots,  enemy bots can only see in a small area around them, watchers can see a long distance upfront, but only in a narrow angle, they alert any enemy bots around you of your location&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level 14, etc will add the rest later ana t3ebl&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Mona Sans VF, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Level ?? transition level, the them turns from light, futuristic and lablike, to dark and cybertronic (I guess)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-100" y="740" width="960" height="650" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
            </root>
        </mxGraphModel>
    </diagram>
